					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="flex flex-row gap-[8vw] justify-center items-center bg-[#FFF8E5] min-h-[26rem] w-full py-12 px-16 max-md:flex-col">
			<div class="text-lg">
				<h2 class="text-3xl max-w-[32rem] font-serif antialiased">
					We're empowering the <span class="underline underline-offset-2 decoration-2 font-bold text-purple-950">community,</span> one problem at a time.
				</h2>
				
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside marker:text-[#370E3D] my-4">
					<li>
						Ensuring the financial security of transactions
					</li>
					<li>
						Promoting professional services
					</li>
					<li>
						Collectivizing artistic resources
					</li>
				</ul>

				<p class="max-w-[32rem]">
					Okay, so what if it’s three problems? Sue us. We embrace challenges and
					turn them into opportunities for greater success.
				</p>	
			</div>
			<div class="shrink-[0.5] max-md:px-16">
				<img class="" src="https://placehold.jp/400x300.png"/>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="bg-white min-h-[14rem] w-full py-12 px-16 max-md:px-2">
			<h1 class="font-serif antialiased font-bold text-3xl text-[#370E3D] text-center">We've made lots (and lots) of clients happy.</h1>
