				</p>	
			</div>
			<div class="shrink-[0.5] max-md:px-16">
				<img class="" src="https://placehold.jp/400x300.png"/>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="bg-[#370E3D] min-h-[26rem] w-full py-12">
