				</h2>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-8 flex flex-row flex-wrap justify-center gap-16 gap-y-8 max-md:flex-col">
				<div class="bg-white max-w-[24rem] px-12 py-6 rounded-2xl max-md:mx-auto">
